{"tid":896695,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Whatsapp研「放假」模式　群組信息自動封存","createTime":"2018-11-10T09:15:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-10T09:29:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf0226ed57591068bc61cac265202e43b3752e77","tid":896695,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:15:54.000Z","msg":"打工仔放假，不少都想避開Whatsapp公司群組的信息轟炸。目前Whatsapp雖然有「靜音」功能，但仍留有一堆「未讀」信息。外國科技網站WABetaInfo最近發現，Whatsapp正研究「放假」模式功能，對打工仔來說可謂喜訊！<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp這個「放假」模式，將容許群組信息自動封存（Archive）。這樣，用家便不會看到未讀的對話，毋須加以理會；該群組亦會處於靜音狀態。<br />\n<br />\n不過，目前尚未知道「放假」模式功能何時面世，估計最快在Whatsapp下次更新時會推出。一般而言，Whatsapp數星期會更新一次。<br />\n<br />\n（獨立報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00005/1541828314675\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00005%2F1541828314675&d=b%2Br2MDSgOkSbTHqQyQqJ4r5jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=60415371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181110%2Fs00005%2F1541828314675&h=b5154836\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181110/s00005/1541828314675</a>"},{"pid":"72cf27d0e13f154c7ddfca9db3c0ad5cb0091fff","tid":896695,"uid":57410,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:20:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知唔係香港本土研發<br />\n如果係香港apps會係研發放假唔應機會自動打電話提醒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29146d6d35c57a1edb13d1ea94f669df2c6a3785","tid":896695,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:22:57.000Z","msg":"咁鐘意放假咪做啲真正有假放既位<br />\n負責operation既不嬲當左自己冇假放架啦"},{"pid":"51456a9cabfafc195d41ce9f398eceed9d8ffed9","tid":896695,"uid":59511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"腦細，邊個唔應機就